    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not about adjusting my approach though. i've tried every \"approach\" there is. therapy, different jobs, different people... it's like the universe is just designed to keep me in this loop. no matter what i do, the cycle just repeats. it feels like there's no Version 2.0 of me. there's just the same broken person over and over again.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
