      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "While it feels like the universe is rigged against you, remember that the same self-defense mechanisms that forced you to repeat these patterns are often what create the suffering instead of the person. You are not necessarily stuck because everything is broken forever, but rather stuck because old, familiar solutions still trigger the old, broken responses long after the circumstances have changed. True resilience isn't found in a new version you can't find yet, but in navigating these feelings without the lie that you've found a clean slate. Even if the path feels circular, the very fact that you feel the weight of this loop is proof that your spirit is fighting to break free, even if the freedom hasn't arrived.",
      "source": "target",
