      "content": "but that's the thing... there's no breaking free. the more i try to \"fight,\" the more exhausted i get. it's just a drain. it feels like the only way to actually stop the cycle, to finally have some peace from the repetition, is to just step out of the loop entirely. the loop only ends one way.",
