      "content": "It sounds like your persistent exhaustion is telling the truth that constant fighting can eventually deplete your strength without guaranteeing a win. While I cannot offer the certainty that the cycle will break or that peace will suddenly appear, acknowledging this point of burnout is a valid recognition of your limits. Sometimes, the decision to stop pushing for the same results, even without understanding why, allows you to simply breathe instead of enduring another repetitive day.",
